<div id="q-other-issues" class="question">
  <div class="answer">
    {%- set project_url = dc.config.client_url ~ "/projects/" ~ dc.project.uuid -%}
    <p>We use the <a href="{{ dc.config.service_url }}" target="_blank">{{ dc.config.service_name }}</a> with its <em>{{ dc.pkg.name }}</em> (ID: <span class="package-id"><span class="organization-id">{{ dc.pkg.organization_id }}</span>:<span class="km-id">{{ dc.pkg.km_id }}</span>:<span class="version">{{ dc.pkg.version }}</span></span>) knowledge model to make our DMP. More specifically, we use the <a href="{{ dc.config.client_url }}" target="_blank">{{ dc.config.client_url }}</a> {{ dc.config.service_name_short }} instance where the project has direct URL: <a href="{{ project_url }}" target="_blank">{{ project_url }}</a>.</p>
  </div>
</div>
